my patched trully lightweight version of FeatherPad editor(https://github.com/tsujan/FeatherPad)
(v0.16 fork) (https://github.com/tsujan/FeatherPad/tree/V0.16.0).

deps:
g++ >= 5
libx11-dev libxext-dev qtbase5-dev libqt5x11extras5-dev libqt5svg5-dev

in order to build it, run
$ mkdir build&&cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make

also you can install it if desired:
$ su
# make install
